<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <center style="width: 300px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;">
        <%= image_tag 'mailresources/logo.png', width: '300', height: '157', alt: 'Midhack 2015', title: 'Midhack 2015' %>
      <h1 style="font: 25px/1.25em 'Duplex Sans', Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3C3C3B;"> <span style="color: #00a6cc;"><%= @new_member.email %> </span> har anmält sig till ditt lag <%= @new_member.team.name %></h1>

      <p style="font: 16px/1.5em 'Duplex Sans', Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3C3C3B;">
        Ditt lag består nu av:
      </p>

      <ul style="list-style-type: none; margin: 30px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 16px/1.5em 'Duplex Sans', Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3C3C3B;">
        <% @team_member_details.each do |teammate| %>
          <li style="margin-top: 10px; line-height: 110%;">
            <a href="mailto:<%= teammate[:email] %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: #00a6cc;" ><%= teammate[:email] %></a>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 0px;"><%= t(".competences.#{teammate[:competence]}") %></p>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>

      <p style="font: 16px/1.5em 'Duplex Sans', Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3C3C3B;">
        Glöm inte att lägga in eventet i kalendern och säga åt dina vänner att gå med i ditt lag.
        Vi syns på Midhack den 14-15 november på Mittuniversitetet campus.
        <a href="mailto:crew@midhack.se" style="color: #00A6CC; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 100;">/Midhack Crew</a>
      </p>
      <a href="<%= @url %>" style="display: block; margin: 1.2em 0;">
        <%= image_tag 'mailresources/moreinfo_sv.png', width: '240', height: '54', alt: 'Mer info', title: 'Mer info' %>
      </a>
      <p style="font: 13px/1.35em 'Duplex Sans', Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3C3C3B;">
        Fått andra planer? <br/>
        <a href="<%= @unsubscribe_url %>" style="color: #00A6CC; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 100;">Avanmäl dig från Midhack</a>
      </p>
    </center>
  </body>
</html>
